Author: Hongrui Duo [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8683-015X>),
    Bo Li [aut] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0001-9944-0003>)
Maintainer: Hongrui Duo <duohongrui@cqnu.edu.cn>
Description: simpipe2docker implements some functions for calling Docker in R
    which can be used for estimating parameters from real data and then simulating
    scRNA-seq data. It is a lightweight R package to download and use, instead of
    configuring complicated programming environment after you have already installed
    Docker and downloaded the simpipe docker image.
URL: https://github.com/duohongrui/simpipe2docker
